				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell is very useful to meditate more safely and not lose your pet like you do with Invisibility.  <BR>
<BR>
I've noticed that Griffins and Cyclops, and possibly others, do still seem to notice you and attack you while using this illusion, so beware.<BR>

				</font>
